OL,7,GThe merger of the BBC News Channel
OL,8,Gand BBC World News is expected to
OL,9,Ghave a soft launch on 6th March.
OL,11,FBut regular viewers will by now be
OL,12,Fused to seeing programmes in the
OL,13,Fevenings and weekends which are
OL,14,Fdesigned for viewers around the globe
OL,15,Fas well as those at home.
OL,3,C"Broadcasting to viewers in the UK
OL,4,Cand around the world, this is BBC
OL,5,CNews"
