OL,7,FIt poses huge editorial dilemmas.
OL,8,F Stories of vital importance and
OL,9,Frelevance to UK viewers may be of
OL,10,Flittle interest or significance
OL,11,Fabroad.  Stories of global importance
OL,12,Fmay seem detached from the lives of
OL,13,Fmost people in the UK.
OL,15,FSaturday's combined output gave a
OL,16,Fgood example.  The Nigerian election
OL,17,Fled the afternoon output.
