OL,7,FIt is important for a public service
OL,8,Fbroadcaster to cover these stories
OL,9,Fand take foreign affairs seriously.
OL,10,FThere are concerns that Africa is
OL,11,Freported all too rarely except in the
OL,12,Fcontext of tragedy.
OL,14,FBut a lead story? It is not a foreign
OL,15,Fstory of direct concern to UK viewers
OL,16,Flike the war in Ukraine. Sky News
OL,17,Fmust have been delighted.
