OL,7,FPerhaps though there is a niche for a
OL,8,Fchannel focused on solid foreign
OL,9,Freporting. Nobody who cares about
OL,10,Fserious international journalism or
OL,11,Fworld affairs would say these stories
OL,12,Fshould not be covered.
OL,14,FThe context in which they appear
OL,15,Fmatters though. Imagine the risk of
OL,16,Flooking aloof and detached from the
OL,17,Fstories so important to licence
OL,18,Fholders.
