OL,7,FIt is unfair to judge the new News
OL,8,FChannel in advance. Yet again, I
OL,9,Fstress international news matters and
OL,10,Fnot just the foreign news likely to
OL,11,Fresonate directly with a UK audience.
OL,13,FBut there must surely be real worries
OL,14,Fover whether the new look channel
OL,15,Fwill still cover a full range of
OL,16,Fdomestic stories properly.
OL,18,FThe jury will be out for several
OL,19,Fweeks.
